Read the firmographic filter (sectors, sizes, locations) currently applied to a lens.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} before adjusting an audience — see what's already restricted so changes are diffs, not full replacements.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} to actually apply changes — use the leadbay_adjust_audience composite, which handles permissions transparently.
